            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              Potentially stupid question:  I'm going to be bottling a batch soon.  After I bottle, do I want to store the bottles at the yeast's ideal fermentation temp, or should I be storing them at a slightly colder temp?  This is an Ale, not a Lager.

              

              
              
