          <td class="post-content">
            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              I don't brew but my brother does.  His Black IPA just took 3rd out of 140-150 entries in a Houston brewers contest.  I tried some....it was flat out awesome, although my favorite still is his smoked porter.  A bunch of his friends and I have been trying to convince him to start selling his brew, but he's resistant to the idea.  He gave me a pony keg of his smoked porter and I had a couple people try it, one of whom is a liquor distributor and another is a bar manager - both wanted to start selling it immediately.  He makes really good money with his current job, but he's good enough to seriously open his own brewery and make millions.  I really wish I had some so poeple could try it.  Next time there's an Ars meet in Fort Worth, I'll have him send a couple kegs and people can try it.  His beer is *ridiculously* good.

              

              
              
            </div>
